description:
This market asks whether Sam Bankman-Fried (SBF) will set foot in the United States between December 13, 2022, and February 15, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET. 

If SBF sets foot in the United States between December 13, 2022 and February 15, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to "Yes". Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No". 

For the purpose of this market, "setting foot in the United States" is defined as SBF physically entering the terrestrial or maritime territory of the United States. Setting foot on US territories such as Guam and Puerto Rico will count for this market. If SBF sets foot in a United States embassy, it will not suffice to resolve this market to "Yes."  Whether or not SBF enters United States airspace during the timeframe of this market will have no bearing on a positive resolution. 

The primary resolution source for this information will be official information from government of the United States of America, however a consensus of credible reporting will also be used.
